Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.10,0:02:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你保護小妙他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.94,0:02:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.98,0:02:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.52,0:02:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是來救這個城市的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.60,0:03:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第九十一話\N蠢動的風水魔力  狙擊神谷道場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救這個城市？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣 帚星防禦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白！淨之脈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.31,0:03:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字叫陣風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大和風水的風之一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.94,0:03:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後他們是水之一神\N放出的式神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.87,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大和風水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是你們的友軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會計師那邊取得證言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.59,0:03:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相關的公司呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再等兩個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給他們一小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎 要搜集更多證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.93,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.73,0:04:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅牛火鍋店提出被害報告書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.54,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說逼迫他們拆遷的要求\N越來越強烈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是風水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.17,0:04:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是辦那件事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論那還是這件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按照賄賂的線索一直追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.35,0:04:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就追到佐伯商會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.35,0:04:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背後人物一定是社長佐伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.92,0:04:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於紅牛火鍋的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.22,0:04:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.66,0:04:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那件事全權給你處理隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 謝長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.10,0:04:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是…佐伯優之進嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.04,0:04:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有很多問題想請教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.51,0:04:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問你救我們的理由是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不喜歡看到有人死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要勉強講理由的話 那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.55,0:04:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 這種說法\N好像我們一點力量也施不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是那麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.12,0:04:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都在呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.52,0:05:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找到個退火的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟大家一起吃怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,署長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯社長的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.07,0:05:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說他在維新以後開店\N一下子就成了暴發戶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.98,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯商會發展得很快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次還鋪起鐵路哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵路？在哪堙H
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在武藏野的雜木林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.96,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武藏野？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.33,0:05:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思\N那麼別管我請先享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.93,0:05:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們與您之間有什麼過節？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.90,0:05:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊那家店的是自古以來\N與我們一族對立的水之一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.67,0:05:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼與他戰鬥\N就是拯救這個城市呢？？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.48,0:06:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在述說那個之前請先看這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是紅牛耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是神谷道場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.16,0:06:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 被用奇怪的星型\N連接起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.86,0:06:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個城市是被\N無數大小的魔法陣所守護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.40,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,製造那個的 是德川家康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德川家康？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從開立幕府以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.64,0:06:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德川家康為了守護\N江戶不受災難侵害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.68,0:06:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而秘密設下魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先建下幾所\N供奉邪那岐神的神社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.92,0:06:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把邪氣封進\N那三點連結的區域內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維持氣的清淨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.66,0:06:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來將那三點與五芒星形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,增加守護的威列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.47,0:06:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著為了維持高純度的氣脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.04,0:06:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還利用山川大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.04,0:07:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是東之青龍隅田川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西之白虎東海道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南之朱雀 江戶灣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,北之靈峰 富士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.42,0:07:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個命名為永恆之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未赤永恆的永恆嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.26,0:07:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而奉將軍命令完成陣式的\N就是我的祖先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.63,0:07:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要設下這個魔法陣\N歷經了許多困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水之一族也想獨自設陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.84,0:07:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此 我們的魔法陣\N理所當然妨礙他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.78,0:07:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此 兩族產生強烈爭執
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.55,0:07:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果 我們一族絕不退讓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.28,0:07:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算把魔法陣完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面被打敗的水之一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就從這個國家消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水之一族又回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.03,0:07:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是發生這次的騷動嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅牛與這個道場\N都是永恆之陣的一部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.04,0:08:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們來加以破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.14,0:08:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表示他們打算設下新的魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.05,0:08:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是讓他們完成新的魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.12,0:08:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會有什麼後果呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個城市…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.82,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這個國家會毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國家會毀滅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只因為設了魔法陣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.49,0:08:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 風之一族的魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.66,0:08:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是為了維持土地上的氣脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制氣脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相對於此水之一族的魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是要自由控制氣脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還可轉為\N攻擊用途的雙刃劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.58,0:08:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大陸為何被捲入\N可憎的鴉片戰爭中呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,英國的侵略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.65,0:08:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鴉片的蔓延
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都只是個開端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原因是他們疏於維持氣脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.86,0:08:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對氣脈控制失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.76,0:09:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今同樣的危機\N造訪我們國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刻不容緩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才你們問我為何救你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說老實話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.74,0:09:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為我知道\N光憑我的力量是不夠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.34,0:09:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村 以及各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.01,0:09:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你們助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們沒空浪費時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.94,0:09:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請快成立\N特別組應付這個事態吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.18,0:09:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為誰會相信這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.21,0:09:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少可以找部省啊\N去問山縣大人怎樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了知道了 我連絡看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.02,0:10:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 那麼也請川路長官去見陣風吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了…\N不對 我幹嘛去見他呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.86,0:10:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川路警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.86,0:10:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報告！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.77,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛得到情報指出\N佐伯商會在武藏野鋪鐵路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵路？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.61,0:10:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些賄賂好像是為了\N讓政府准許這件工程而鋪路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.18,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩…為什麼海運跟不動產公司\N要鋪起鐵路來呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定有什麼問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.19,0:10:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.95,0:10:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不出結論時就休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天一定要來神谷道場哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓民間公司來鋪鐵路？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 有辦法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.81,0:10:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是請教英國的技師\N才學會這門技術的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.51,0:10:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民間企業不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 如果有去過大陸\N或許可能哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.48,0:11:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大陸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.95,0:11:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說英國人\N正在那邊大鋪鐵路呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.42,0:11:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大陸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼做\N水井的紅水就會復原嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.81,0:11:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個土地下面有強大的氣流過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦受到破壞\N這種程度的處置還不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,災難必需由根拔除才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.78,0:11:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水之一族為什麼又回來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.19,0:11:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為德川政府倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.46,0:11:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且新政府為了\N去年的西南戰爭而又疲憊不堪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.70,0:11:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是重新設陣的好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可笑呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.17,0:11:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以風水推動世界的時代\N應該隨著德川消失了呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.17,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何沒有拋棄風水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們風水師不知道\N別的生存之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.74,0:12:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每一族都為了風水賭命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.68,0:12:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也為此失去了性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是即使這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.25,0:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生為風水師的人\N還是要繼續為風水而活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是宿命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算成為最後一人 我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.79,0:12:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算被時代拋下\N只剩下毀滅之道也不管？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.93,0:12:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宿命 即是「道」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.07,0:12:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而風水 是自然之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果毀滅是「道」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.44,0:12:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我何必反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.65,0:12:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快一點…進度太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.06,0:12:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能再快了 社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.13,0:12:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,增加人手\N總之必需照預定計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.75,0:13:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這婺T止進入 快點離開柵欄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.58,0:13:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我不是可疑人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.62,0:13:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽說來這堨i以找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.55,0:13:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 是來找工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.56,0:13:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那邊找辦理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.26,0:13:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問為什麼要在\N這麼偏僻的地方開鐵路呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道上面的想法啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.17,0:13:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說是要挖鐵路\N卻是在挖洞挖隧道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隧道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯優之進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有必要查他的來歷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.72,0:13:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.02,0:13:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在道場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.75,0:13:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他好像在想事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他把那個風水師講的話當真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做好人也因該有限度嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.96,0:13:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.13,0:14:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子早點睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我 放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要回去\N我幹嘛來找風水師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.38,0:14:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都到這堣F\N你也太不乾脆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.45,0:14:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川路大人\N署長你們怎麼在雨中爭執起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.86,0:14:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉老是來打擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.36,0:14:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想讓川路也知道那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風先生 你就長話短說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.97,0:14:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川路警察官！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.54,0:14:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失禮了 請問…\N昨天提到的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼看法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.61,0:14:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說警視廳追查的\N佐伯企業家的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說了嗎？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.38,0:14:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,署長說的沒錯佐伯\N與破壞永恆之陣一事有關聯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 佐伯是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是單純的小賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來不想幫助警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那位署長說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.26,0:15:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯現在正從事\N與賺錢無關的鐵路工程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.87,0:15:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我當然知道 你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.47,0:15:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,津南是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你查出什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯他另有目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在鐵道的另一邊開大隧道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.68,0:15:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隧道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.22,0:15:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.32,0:15:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武藏野有回流到龍脈的巨大水泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.96,0:15:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武藏野是支配\N關東氣脈的重要起點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在那堳鶿}的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以控制囤積在\N水泉的強大龍脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一口氣注入府內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是那麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.84,0:15:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護關東的永恆之陣\N會瞬間瓦解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.01,0:15:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.81,0:16:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 佐伯與風水\N到底有什麼關聯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然有關聯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.32,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就我調查 佐伯是大陸來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.29,0:16:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且出現在紅牛的風水師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.49,0:16:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用的是火炎之技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.93,0:16:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在風水世界中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制火炎的\N是屬於大陸風水那一系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.07,0:16:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大陸風水師？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯在大陸與那些人聯手嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯優之進這個名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.44,0:16:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是來日本以後才捏造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他本名是幽水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是查出這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.38,0:16:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水之族的人名字最後\N一定有個「水」字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯是水之族的後裔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你說都是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.82,0:16:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼270年前\N他們就是逃去大陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.83,0:16:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那種地方融入了大陸風水術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川路…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可小看風水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.30,0:16:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是明、唐、不\N是更早以前就治理大陸的法術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.01,0:17:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用方法不得當\N就會毀滅一國的兩刃劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可疑的拆除騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.72,0:17:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,府內的天變地異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及風水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.22,0:17:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來三個無關的事件\N都產生關聯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.93,0:17:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.33,0:17:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我的力量微薄\N但是請讓我幫助你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.47,0:17:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 劍心\N你的壞毛病又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.17,0:17:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助\N我是再三考慮後決定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.31,0:17:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅牛跟神谷道場都被當成目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能置之不管的
